			<h3>Gym innovations</h3>
				<article id="index-article1">
					<header>
						<h3> Fitness Apps </h3>
					</header>
					<figure>
						<a href="product.html"> <img src="img/fitness-apps.jpg" alt="Tablet showing information from punching bag" title="tablet showing sports data"> </a>
						<figcaption>Fig.1 - copyright <a href="https://www.bookeeapp.com/articles/8-fitness-technologies">Bookee</a></figcaption>
					</figure>
					<p>
						A new technology thats being used more and more are fitness apps, these apps collect data from fitness equipment and show it to the user. 
						Data that is being collected can vary from diet charts and monitoring to tracking footsteps and heartrate &#40;connected with a wearable device ofcourse&#41;.
						These apps use technologies such as artificial intelligence and machine learning to further perfect the information they give to either a coach or clients.
					</p>
					<footer class="article-footer">
						<a href="https://www.bookeeapp.com/articles/8-fitness-technologies" target="_blank"> More info</a>
					</footer>
				</article>
				
				<article id="index-article2">
					<header>
						<h3> Smart gym equipment </h3>
					</header>
					<figure>
						<a href="product.html"> <img src="img/smart-equipment.jpg" alt="Threadmill with digital interface" title="smart threadmill"> </a>
						<figcaption>Fig.2 - copyright <a href="https://www.technogym.com/nl-NL/home-gym/">Technogym</a></figcaption>
					</figure>
					<p>
						These new gym machines are equipped with more than just the functions to train, they will also show you how well you are training using a digital interface. 
						Where the fitness apps will create training schemes and diet patterns, these machines will monitor things like heartrate time training or distanced run.
						The newest of these machines can also connect to smart apps and show records and progress.
					</p>
					<footer class="article-footer">
						<a href="https://www.technogym.com/nl-NL/home-gym/" target="_blank"> More info</a>
					</footer>
				</article>
				
