					</figure>
					<p>
						Don&#39;t want to rely on specific gym hours or are you to shy to go to the gym&#63; 
						Maybe online coaching is the thing for you, the services can be live or a video so a 24&#47;7 service is guaranteed, 
						the rates for a lesson are also lower than its physical counterpart.
					</p>
					<footer class="article-footer">
